## Athletic Teams  

The **Crusaders** field 27 varsity sports, competing at NCAA Division I level. [[74](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/College_sports)] Key affiliations include:  

* **Patriot League** – all sports except football, which competes in the **Atlantic Hockey America** conference. [[75](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Atlantic_Hockey_America)]  
* **Hockey East** – for both men’s and women’s ice hockey. [[76](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hockey_East)]  
* **NCAA Division I** – with football competing in the **Football Championship Subdivision**. [[77](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/NCAA_Division_I)]  

Facilities include **Fitton Field** (football stadium), **Hart Recreation Center**, **Linda Johnson Smith Soccer Stadium**, and the **Hart Ice Rink**. [[78](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fitton_Field)]  

